        "remove_horizontal_spacing": false,
        "liquid": "<!-- ============================================================\n     CUSTOMER REVIEWS ‚Äî standalone block (paste into \"Custom Liquid\")\n     To edit a review: duplicate an <article class=\"ps-review-card\">\n     and change the image, rating (1-5), quote and name.\n     ============================================================ -->\n<style>\n  .ps-reviews{--ps-bg:#f4efe6;--ps-card-bg:#fff;--ps-text:#3a3530;--ps-muted:#8a8378;--ps-star:#2e8b57;padding:56px 0;background:var(--ps-bg)}\n  .ps-reviews__inner{max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 20px}\n  .ps-reviews__heading{text-align:center;font-size:clamp(22px,3vw,32px);margin:0 0 6px;color:var(--ps-text)}\n  .ps-reviews__subheading{text-align:center;color:var(--ps-muted);margin:0 0 32px;font-size:15px}\n  .ps-reviews__track{display:grid;grid-auto-flow:column;grid-auto-columns:92%;gap:18px;overflow-x:auto;scroll-snap-type:x mandatory;-webkit-overflow-scrolling:touch;padding-bottom:8px;scrollbar-width:none}\n  .ps-reviews__track::-webkit-scrollbar{display:none}\n  @media (min-width:600px){.ps-reviews__track{grid-auto-columns:calc(50% - 9px)}}\n  @media (min-width:1000px){.ps-reviews__track{grid-auto-columns:calc(33.333% - 12px)}}\n  .ps-review-card{scroll-snap-align:start;background:var(--ps-card-bg);border-radius:18px;padding:20px;box-shadow:0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,.07);display:flex;flex-direction:column}\n  .ps-review-card__media{border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:16px;aspect-ratio:4/3;background:#eee}\n  .ps-review-card__img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block}\n  .ps-review-card__stars{display:flex;gap:3px;margin-bottom:10px}\n  .ps-star{width:20px;height:20px}\n  .ps-star--full{fill:var(--ps-star)}\n  .ps-star--empty{fill:#e2ddd3}\n  .ps-review-card__verified{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;font-size:14px;color:var(--ps-muted);margin-bottom:14px}\n  .ps-check{width:15px;height:15px;fill:var(--ps-star)}\n  .ps-review-card__quote{font-size:17px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--ps-text);margin:0 0 18px;flex:1}\n  .ps-review-card__author{font-weight:600;font-size:16px;color:var(--ps-text);margin:0}\n</style>\n\n<section class=\"ps-reviews\" aria-label=\"Customer reviews\">\n  <div class=\"ps-reviews__inner\">\n\n    <h2 class=\"ps-reviews__heading\">What our customers are saying</h2>\n    <p class=\"ps-reviews__subheading\">Verified reviews</p>\n\n    <div class=\"ps-reviews__track\">\n\n      <!-- REVIEW 1 -->\n      <article class=\"ps-review-card\">\n        <div class=\"ps-review-card__media\">\n          <img class=\"ps-review-card__img\" loading=\"lazy\" src=https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1076/7378/0573/files/photo_fit.webp?v=1783114214alt=\"Customer review\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ps-review-card__stars\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" class=\"ps-star ps-star--full\"><path d=\"M10 1.5l2.6 5.6 6.1.6-4.6 4.2 1.3 6-5.4-3.1-5.4 3.1 1.3-6-4.6-4.2 6.1-.6z\"/></svg>\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" class=\"ps-star ps-star--full\"><path d=\"M10 1.5l2.6 5.6 6.1.6-4.6 4.2 1.3 6-5.4-3.1-5.4 3.1 1.3-6-4.6-4.2 6.1-.6z\"/></svg>\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" class=\"ps-star ps-star--full\"><path d=\"M10 1.5l2.6 5.6 6.1.6-4.6 4.2 1.3 6-5.4-3.1-5.4 3.1 1.3-6-4.6-4.2 6.1-.6z\"/></svg>\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" class=\"ps-star ps-star--full\"><path d=\"M10 1.5l2.6 5.6 6.1.6-4.6 4.2 1.3 6-5.4-3.1-5.4 3.1 1.3-6-4.6-4.2 6.1-.6z\"/></svg>\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" class=\"ps-star ps-star--full\"><path d=\"M10 1.5l2.6 5.6 6.1.6-4.6 4.2 1.3 6-5.4-3.1-5.4 3.1 1.3-6-4.6-4.2 6.1-.6z\"/></svg>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ps-review-card__verified\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" class=\"ps-check\"><path d=\"M7.5 13.5L4 10l1.4-1.4 2.1 2.1 5.1-5.1L14 7z\"/></svg>\n          Verified purchase\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"ps-review-card__quote\">&#8220;I’m actually getting emotional looking at these side-by-side because I remember exactly how I felt in that first photo. Just stuck and uncomfortable. For so long, I felt like a stranger in my own skin, always hiding behind baggy clothes. But seeing this change... You have no idea how much it means to just feel 'light' and comfortable in your own body for once I'd recommend it.&#8221;</p>\n        <p class=\"ps-review-card__author\">Mary L., 44.</p>\n      </article>\n\n      <!-- REVIEW 2 -->\n      <article class=\"ps-review-card\">\n        <div class=\"ps-review-card__media\">\n          <img class=\"ps-review-card__img\" loading=\"lazy\" src=https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1076/7378/0573/files/ChatGPT_Image_Jul_1_2026_10_58_16_PM.png?v=1782939533alt=\"Customer review\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ps-review-card__stars\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" class=\"ps-star ps-star--full\"><path d=\"M10 1.5l2.6 5.6 6.1.6-4.6 4.2 1.3 6-5.4-3.1-5.4 3.1 1.3-6-4.6-4.2 6.1-.6z\"/></svg>\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" class=\"ps-star ps-star--full\"><path d=\"M10 1.5l2.6 5.6 6.1.6-4.6 4.2 1.3 6-5.4-3.1-5.4 3.1 1.3-6-4.6-4.2 6.1-.6z\"/></svg>\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" class=\"ps-star ps-star--full\"><path d=\"M10 1.5l2.6 5.6 6.1.6-4.6 4.2 1.3 6-5.4-3.1-5.4 3.1 1.3-6-4.6-4.2 6.1-.6z\"/></svg>\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" class=\"ps-star ps-star--full\"><path d=\"M10 1.5l2.6 5.6 6.1.6-4.6 4.2 1.3 6-5.4-3.1-5.4 3.1 1.3-6-4.6-4.2 6.1-.6z\"/></svg>\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" class=\"ps-star ps-star--full\"><path d=\"M10 1.5l2.6 5.6 6.1.6-4.6 4.2 1.3 6-5.4-3.1-5.4 3.1 1.3-6-4.6-4.2 6.1-.6z\"/></svg>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ps-review-card__verified\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" class=\"ps-check\"><path d=\"M7.5 13.5L4 10l1.4-1.4 2.1 2.1 5.1-5.1L14 7z\"/></svg>\n          Verified purchase\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"ps-review-card__quote\">&#8220;My GP put it down to 'just menopause' and left it there. I felt like I'd stopped being taken seriously about my own body. This has quietly proved otherwise.&#8221;</p>\n        <p class=\"ps-review-card__author\">— Angela R., 51.</p>\n      </article>\n\n      <!-- REVIEW 3 -->\n      <article class=\"ps-review-card\">\n        <div class=\"ps-review-card__media\">\n          <img class=\"ps-review-card__img\" loading=\"lazy\" src=https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1076/7378/0573/files/Screenshot_2026-06-29_at_9.46.37_PM.png?v=1782937819 alt=\"Customer review\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ps-review-card__stars\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" class=\"ps-star ps-star--full\"><path d=\"M10 1.5l2.6 5.6 6.1.6-4.6 4.2 1.3 6-5.4-3.1-5.4 3.1 1.3-6-4.6-4.2 6.1-.6z\"/></svg>\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" class=\"ps-star ps-star--full\"><path d=\"M10 1.5l2.6 5.6 6.1.6-4.6 4.2 1.3 6-5.4-3.1-5.4 3.1 1.3-6-4.6-4.2 6.1-.6z\"/></svg>\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" class=\"ps-star ps-star--full\"><path d=\"M10 1.5l2.6 5.6 6.1.6-4.6 4.2 1.3 6-5.4-3.1-5.4 3.1 1.3-6-4.6-4.2 6.1-.6z\"/></svg>\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" class=\"ps-star ps-star--full\"><path d=\"M10 1.5l2.6 5.6 6.1.6-4.6 4.2 1.3 6-5.4-3.1-5.4 3.1 1.3-6-4.6-4.2 6.1-.6z\"/></svg>\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" class=\"ps-star ps-star--full\"><path d=\"M10 1.5l2.6 5.6 6.1.6-4.6 4.2 1.3 6-5.4-3.1-5.4 3.1 1.3-6-4.6-4.2 6.1-.6z\"/></svg>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ps-review-card__verified\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" class=\"ps-check\"><path d=\"M7.5 13.5L4 10l1.4-1.4 2.1 2.1 5.1-5.1L14 7z\"/></svg>\n          Verified purchase\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"ps-review-card__quote\">&#8220;I've tried everything before Phytoseedlabs, diet changes, HRT (which I've found caused more bloating), probiotics, cutting out entire food groups. Nothing worked.  I've been bloated after every single meal for years. 3 weeks on this and my stomach actually feels calm for the first time in forever. I wish I'd found this natural helper sooner..&#8221;</p>\n        <p class=\"ps-review-card__author\">— Helen T., 54</p>\n      </article>\n\n      <!-- REVIEW 4 -->\n      <article class=\"ps-review-card\">\n        <div class=\"ps-review-card__media\">\n          <img class=\"ps-review-card__img\" loading=\"lazy\" src=https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1076/7378/0573/files/ChatGPT_Image_Jul_1_2026_11_02_53_PM.png?v=1782939822 alt=\"Customer review\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ps-review-card__stars\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" class=\"ps-star ps-star--full\"><path d=\"M10 1.5l2.6 5.6 6.1.6-4.6 4.2 1.3 6-5.4-3.1-5.4 3.1 1.3-6-4.6-4.2 6.1-.6z\"/></svg>\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" class=\"ps-star ps-star--full\"><path d=\"M10 1.5l2.6 5.6 6.1.6-4.6 4.2 1.3 6-5.4-3.1-5.4 3.1 1.3-6-4.6-4.2 6.1-.6z\"/></svg>\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" class=\"ps-star ps-star--full\"><path d=\"M10 1.5l2.6 5.6 6.1.6-4.6 4.2 1.3 6-5.4-3.1-5.4 3.1 1.3-6-4.6-4.2 6.1-.6z\"/></svg>\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" class=\"ps-star ps-star--full\"><path d=\"M10 1.5l2.6 5.6 6.1.6-4.6 4.2 1.3 6-5.4-3.1-5.4 3.1 1.3-6-4.6-4.2 6.1-.6z\"/></svg>\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" class=\"ps-star ps-star--full\"><path d=\"M10 1.5l2.6 5.6 6.1.6-4.6 4.2 1.3 6-5.4-3.1-5.4 3.1 1.3-6-4.6-4.2 6.1-.6z\"/></svg>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ps-review-card__verified\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" class=\"ps-check\"><path d=\"M7.5 13.5L4 10l1.4-1.4 2.1 2.1 5.1-5.1L14 7z\"/></svg>\n          Verified purchase\n        </div>\n        <p class=\"ps-review-card__quote\">&#8220;If you know the struggle of having to unbutton your jeans under the table at dinner because your bloating is so painful, you need this. I'd stopped wearing anything tight because I hated the shape of my belly when I was bloated. I was skeptical about oregano oil, but Phytoseed Labs is the only thing that has actually flattened the bloat and let me wear what I want without fear. It's a total game-changer for my confidence.&#8221;</p>\n        <p class=\"ps-review-card__author\">Claire D., 46</p>\n      </article>\n\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>",
